        "subject": "LU-17813 build: prefer UTS_RELEASE over uname -r",
        "message": "LU-17813 build: prefer UTS_RELEASE over uname -r\n\nIn a container 'uname -r' reports the hosts kernel\nInstead we should use the kernel version that is being\nconfigured: $UTS_RELEASE\n\nOnce UTS_RELEASE is available prefer it over uname -r\n\nHPE-bug-id: LUS-12323\nFixes: b83156304df (\"LU-17254 lnet: Fix ofed detection with specific kernel version\")\nSigned-off-by: Shaun Tancheff <shaun.tancheff@hpe.com>\nChange-Id: Ib835b96f46086454c894ec1c3e5ae1550ab2a245\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
